data.description: Wait no longer... NEW ON THE MARKET...This lovely home is tucked away in the highly desirable community of ‘The Trees.’ Pull into your detached 2-car garage with recent epoxy flooring that leads to your stone-paved private courtyard entry. The beautifully paved courtyard welcomes you home. Step into your open floorplan with lots of natural light. Enjoy entertaining on your back patio day or night the vibe is right. The living room exhibits a cozy fireplace and dining area,  View the courtyard from the kitchen. Lots of closet space upstairs. What? There's a Juliet balcony in the master bedroom where you can overlook the private back patio. With a short distance to horse trails, jogging trails, sports parks, food dining, and more. The Trees community a quite a gem. Showings are by appointment. Schedule a private tour today.
